<collectingCountry box="[1236,1387,431,457]" name="United States of America" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">United States</collectingCountry>
National Museum that had been compared to LeConte’s type by Doris Blake. This 
<collectionCode box="[1049,1130,467,493]" country="USA" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34871" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:34871" name="Smithsonian Institution, National Museum of Natural History" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" type="Museum">USNM</collectionCode>
